  note = {The Progressive Access project provides interactive chemical diagrams that are accessible across devices. The site describes features such as keyboard and menu-driven exploration, magnification, high-contrast and different colour schemes. An automated conversion workflow generates accessible SVG diagrams that work with screen readers:contentReference[oaicite:41]\{index=41\}.}
